des: Web Cidade was an idea founded in 2024 to bring a different experience of listening to the radio. The initial idea was to create a channel that could play the music of the moment, without following the traditional "market models", but with the "real" concept of "more music and less chat"; an idea founded on the fact that there are no alternative adult programming stations that are not commercial without all that blah, blah, blah.
